1080\u002F1364557032000119616",pubMedLink:a}]},{id:"ref4",displayNumber:a,existInContent:c,content:"\u003Cspan class=\"string-name\"\u003E\u003Cspan class=\"surname\"\u003EBaril\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E, \u003Cspan class=\"given-names\"\u003EA\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E and \u003Cspan class=\"string-name\"\u003E\u003Cspan class=\"surname\"\u003ESilverman\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E, \u003Cspan class=\"given-names\"\u003EM\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E (\u003Cspan class=\"year\"\u003E2022\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E) \u003Cspan class=\"article-title\"\u003EForgotten lives: trans older adults living with dementia at the intersection of cisgenderism, ableism\u002Fcogniticism and ageism\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E. \u003Cspan class=\"source\"\u003ESexualities\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E \u003Cspan class=\"volume\"\u003E25\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E, \u003Cspan class=\"fpage\"\u003E117\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E–\u003Cspan class=\"lpage\"\u003E131\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E.\u003Ca class='ref-link' target='_blank' aria-label='CrossRef link for Forgotten lives: trans older adults living with dementia at the intersection of cisgenderism, ableism\u002Fcogniticism and ageism' href=https:\u002F\u002Fdx.doi.org\u002F10.1177\u002F1363460719876835\u003ECrossRef\u003C\u002Fa\u003E\u003Ca class='ref-link' target='_blank' aria-label='Google Scholar link for Forgotten lives: trans older adults living with dementia at the intersection of cisgenderism, ableism\u002Fcogniticism and ageism' href=https:\u002F\u002Fscholar.google.com\u002Fscholar_lookup?title=Forgotten+lives%3A+trans+older+adults+living+with+dementia+at+the+intersection+of+cisgenderism%2C+ableism%2Fcogniticism+and+ageism&author=Baril+A&author=Silverman+M&publication+year=2022&journal=Sexualities&volume=25&doi=10.1177%2F1363460719876835&pages=117-131\u003EGoogle Scholar\u003C\u002Fa\u003E",item:[{googleScholarLink:"https:\u002F\u002Fscholar.google.com\u002Fscholar_lookup?title=Forgotten+lives%3A+trans+older+adults+living+with+dementi